TopicTitle: KSP stock replicas: f-22, f-35, su-t50 and more!

Articles.Content:
hello! I've been making a bunch of stock replicas, and uploading videos on youtube. So now I've decided to expand to the forums!

the crafts I have made are:

f-4 phantom

f-15 eagle

f-16 fighting falcon

f-18 hornet

f-22 raptor

f-35 lighting

Su-35

Su t-50/ sukhoi pak fa

harrier jump jet

euro-fighter typhoon

download link here:

[https://www./folder/jeaoprnhdh2m1/ksp_crafts](https://www./folder/jeaoprnhdh2m1/ksp_crafts)

<iframe width="480" height="270" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/soBj7OlcYAE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe>

f-22 and the sukhoi pak fa

enjoy ![:D](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif)

here is my youtube channel if you wanna check that out to

[https://www.youtube.com/user/StealthxxAssassinxx/](https://www.youtube.com/user/StealthxxAssassinxx/)
I really like your use of parts! Keeping it simple and still trying to evoke the shapes of the original is tough to do.
